---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy App – Klikkr Pro" currentPage="" lang="en">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-50 font-sans p-6 md:p-12 lg:p-24 selection:bg-emerald-500/30">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-12">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="space-y-6 pb-12 border-b border-zinc-800/50">
        <a href="/en" class="inline-flex items-center text-zinc-400 hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors text-sm font-medium group">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mr-2 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
          Back to klikkr.ch
        </a>
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 font-medium">Klikkr Pro Companion App (Android & iOS)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-sm text-zinc-500 bg-zinc-900/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800/50">
          <span>Effective Date: March 24, 2026</span>
          <span class="hidden sm:inline">•</span>
          <a href="mailto:support@klikkr.ch" class="hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">support@klikkr.ch</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="space-y-12">

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50">1. Data Controller</h2>
          <div class="p-6 bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-2xl leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-emerald-400">Wild Tec</strong> (Sole Proprietorship)<br />
            Owner: Andri Wild<br />
            Im Baumgarten 4<br />
            6252 Dagmersellen, Switzerland<br />
            UID: CHE-386.932.040<br /><br />
            <strong>Email:</strong>{' '}
            <a href="mailto:support@klikkr.ch" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">support@klikkr.ch</a>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50">2. Core Principle</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            The Klikkr Pro app is built with a <strong class="text-emerald-400">privacy-first approach</strong>.
            The app does not collect, transmit, or store any personal data on external servers.
            There are no user accounts, no cloud sync, and no tracking analytics.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50">3. Local Storage Only</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
            All match data, scores, settings, and paired wristbands are stored
            <strong>strictly locally</strong> on your device.
            No data is transmitted to external servers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50">4. Required Permissions</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
            To function as a display and remote control for the Klikkr Pro wristbands,
            the app requires the following device permissions:
          </p>

          <div class="grid gap-6">
            <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 p-6 rounded-2xl">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Bluetooth (BLE)</h3>
              <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                This permission is essential. It allows your phone to discover, connect to,
                and exchange score data with the Klikkr Pro hardware beacons via Bluetooth Low Energy.
                No Bluetooth data is shared with third parties.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 p-6 rounded-2xl">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Camera</h3>
              <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                The camera is used exclusively for the built-in QR code scanner. This allows you to
                quickly pair Bluetooth devices (MAC addresses) without manually searching through
                the Bluetooth device list. The camera is only activated when you explicitly open the
                scanner. No images or videos are captured or stored.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 p-6 rounded-2xl">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Location (Android 11 and older only)</h3>
              <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                On older Android versions, scanning for nearby Bluetooth devices requires
                the "Fine Location" permission due to the underlying system architecture.
              </p>
              <p class="text-zinc-300 font-medium mt-2">
                We do not determine, read, store, or share your physical location at any time.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50">5. No Third-Party Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
            The Klikkr Pro app does not share any data with third parties. There are no
            ad networks, analytics tools, crash reporting services, or any other
            third-party integrations. Your usage remains entirely private.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50">6. Data Deletion</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
            Since all data is stored exclusively on your device,
            simply uninstalling the app permanently deletes all associated data.
            No data remains on external servers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50">7. Contact for Privacy Concerns</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
            If you have any questions or concerns about privacy, you can reach us at any time:
          </p>
          <div class="p-6 bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-2xl">
            <a href="mailto:support@klikkr.ch" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors font-medium text-lg">
              support@klikkr.ch
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4 pb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50">8. Changes</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
            We reserve the right to update this privacy policy as needed.
            The current version is always available at this address.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
